{
  "stem": "24397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Even though he was, as I mentioned, very religious, my dad was kind of the amateur photographer who, despite of the orthodoxy, was allowed to take a flash picture, which in those days was lighting a piece of paper and the things kind of exploding and providing the light for this time exposure.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody's eyes were closed except my dad's.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were wide open waiting for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we lived in a, in a big old apartment building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, many of those old apartment buildings in Vienna had entrances that were high and wide that could allow a horse and cart fully laden with all kinds of things to go through it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the place where we lived, it was necessary to do that because way behind there, there were cowsheds and, I think, about 15 cows.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a dairy downstairs that sold milk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, they had traffic going in and out with food and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I used to help out in this cow shed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I used to love playing-- working with the horses, grooming them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and just helping out there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a good, good kind of pastime.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very close.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially with my father, because he was there all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for him to get out, we could only do that with great, a great deal of difficulty.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, you know, we didn't have elevators in the, in the building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't-- we didn't have a car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was only on special occasions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we went somewhere, I used to have to go and-- to the taxi rank and bring a taxi home and look for one that had the lowest steps so he could get into it.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
